'''2017年巴布亞紐幾內亞地震'''發生於2017年1月22日上午4點30分（UTC），地震規模達7.9。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2017/01/22/asia/papua-new-guinea-quake/index.html|title=Magnitude 7.9 quake strikes off Papua New Guinea|last=CNN|first=Joe Sutton and Susannah Cullinane|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2017-01-22|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125025321/https://www.cnn.com/2017/01/22/asia/papua-new-guinea-quake/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-papua-quake-idUSKBN15605Y|title=Powerful quake strikes off Papua New Guinea, initial tsunami alert wound back|date=2017-01-22|agency=Reuters|accessdate=2017-01-22|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128103350/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-papua-quake-idUSKBN15605Y|dead-url=no}}</ref>至6點39分，[[太平洋海嘯警報中心|太平洋海嘯警報中心]]確認無海嘯威脅後，解除海嘯警報。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ptwc.weather.gov/ptwc/text.php?id=pacific.TSUPAC.2017.01.22.0641|title=TSUNAMI MESSAGE NUMBER 5|access-date=22 January 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170124154211/https://ptwc.weather.gov/ptwc/text.php?id=pacific.TSUPAC.2017.01.22.0641|archive-date=2017-01-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>[[布干维尔岛|布干维尔岛]][[阿拉瓦_(巴布亚新几内亚)|阿拉瓦]]受到些許損害，[[布卡_(巴布亚新几内亚)|布卡]]則有[[停電|停電]]發生。<ref>{{cite web|author=Rod Mcguirk|title=Strong quake hits Solomons; some damage but no tsunami|url=http://www.dailyrepublicannews.com/news/20170122/strong-quake-hits-solomons-some-damage-but-no-tsunami|agency=Associated Press|via=[[The_Daily_Republican|The Daily Republican]]|accessdate=22 January 2017|date=22 January 2017|archive-date=2019-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190902223107/http://www.dailyrepublicannews.com/news/20170122/strong-quake-hits-solomons-some-damage-but-no-tsunami|dead-url=no}}</ref>

